Hey,
Our path planner was being extremely weird and even though we’ve deleted certain auton rountines, it still shows those same paths. Our deploy/pathplanner/autos directory shows:

IMG_95633024×4032 3.09 MB

However,
Our autonchooser sendableChooser on our shuffleboard shows:
IMG_95613024×4032 3.87 MB

IMG_95623024×4032 4.44 MB

I can’t figure out how to get rid of these autos and help would be much appreciated.
Thank you!
Team 3984

From my experience, I’ve found that sometimes the WPIlib deploy pipeline doesn’t do a great job deleting things on the roboRIO. You may find it helpful to manually ssh to the rio, and then delete everything in /home/lvuser/deploy
